Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.64,0:00:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the only way to save both Mai and me....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is for me to bet everything on this draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was the image just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you saying that I'm the last person to be chosen by the Nameless Dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I sense limitless possibility hidden in this card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.92,0:00:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please lend me your power, Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.74,0:00:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:02:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Miracle of Hermos"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermos! Please lend me your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as what Yugi has!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.54,0:02:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} was chosen as a True Duelist by the Legendary Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be... Jounouchi got the power of the Legendary Dragons, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.09,0:02:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we underestimated this guy too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This means he's a stronger Duelist than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Claw of Hermos"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard a' that card before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.14,0:02:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be one of the rare cards he got from Pegasus!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only {\i1}him{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's total favoritism~!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.06,0:02:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and the others will....!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power hasn't been cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to undo the locks using this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.75,0:03:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That card....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.87,0:03:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can feel a strong power coming from it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What exactly...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.42,0:03:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.97,0:03:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll revive Magical Gigacyber!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know that Gigacyber, with only 2200 Attack Points,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stands no chance against my Harpy's Pet Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll bet on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I Summon Time Magician in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate the Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermos can transform into an Equipment Card for any Monster on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm counting on you, Hermos!\N Create a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.87,0:04:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's {\i1}that{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}was{\i0} a wee bit curious as to what was gonna show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what're ya trying to prove\N by bringing that {\i1}toy{\i0} out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that its strongest form?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi! Are you sure you weren't mistaken?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.72,0:04:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can sense Hermos's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter if it doesn't look cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I don't know the power of this weapon, I have no choice but to use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.11,0:04:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I equip Time Magic Hammer with Gigacyber!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Magic Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have enough Attack Power, yet he's going to strike with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's more to it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Claw of Hermos...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No matter what you try to do, it won't work on me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpy Lady Pharaoh Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way, even if Gigacyber's Attack is lifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the attack damage is 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no flaw in my strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up those numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.... nothing seems to have changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you gravely miscalculated the strength of the Legendary Dragons!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of me, Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, you really {\i1}aren't{\i0} going to fight me seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this ridiculous Duel right this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.05,0:06:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters....!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}'s Monsters disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.15,0:06:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is destroying the Monsters\N part of Hermos's power...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's all....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be more to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That space twilight-like vortex is still on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to my Harpies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card! Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened, but since Mai's field is empty, now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigacyber, Direct Attack Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry....!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, he's a Duelist chosen by the Legendary Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set one card face-down! Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just a little longer and I can end this in a tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That way both of us can be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Must not lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten much stronger...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have obtained Doma's power...! So I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai's Monster is back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The number that appeared then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent's Monsters will be sent to the future turns by Time Magic Hammer according to the numbers they are assigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it is set for next turn, it'll return in the next turn, and if it's set for six turns, the Monster will return on the sixth turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:09:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the player can start over fresh and prepare for an attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the Effect when Time Magician and Hermos are fused together into Time Magic Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And because Harpy Lady hasn't returned to the field yet, Harpy's Pet Dragon's Attack will drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it still has more than Gigacyber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back...! My Monster's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right...! I won't lose...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll {\i1}win{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpy's Pet Dragon! Attack Gigacyber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.79,0:09:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She lost her cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Card open! Devil Dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card reduces the enemy Monster's Attack by the amount rolled on the dice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dude!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:10:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Attack Points of Harpy's Pet Dragon is reduced by half!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I want to {\i1}win{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}have{\i0} to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good. If this keeps up...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.86,0:10:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shard of the Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.57,0:10:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Release your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boundary disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:10:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was far too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Orichalcos protects us, if we try to release the boundary against its will, it may no longer shield our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't let her continue like this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.03,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet, I'll be taking your soul, O great Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The locks should open now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...! What happened to Mai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DAMN IT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.46,0:12:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MAI!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Mai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.93,0:12:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know that for sure yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.58,0:12:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you tying to cover up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.58,0:12:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.50,0:12:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really fought Jounouchi in order to steal his soul...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.27,0:13:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus called us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Pegasus okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we got here, he already...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.63,0:13:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Mai Kujaku joined forces with Doma and stole Pegasus's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say Doma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, do you know about Doma too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother just fought a guy from Doma called Amelda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.02,0:13:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy impersonated Pegasus, and set Big Brother into a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.82,0:13:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We pretty much took each other out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we were all called here by Pegasus, relating to the same incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus was able to sense this coming crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to talk to Yugi boy personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I cannot leave this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.80,0:14:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am being watched by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He knew he was in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Pegasus we're talking about. He must have planned two or even three steps ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For his Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.73,0:14:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The card Pegasus sent me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus must have left some clues for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.70,0:14:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was one room I couldn't unlock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Take us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.46,0:14:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just as arrogant as ever...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.46,0:14:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.59,0:14:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ignorin' us like we don't exist...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That in itself is in our favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.31,0:15:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be some rare cards hidden in Pegasus's hidden room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.50,0:15:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only door I couldn't unlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a trap Doma set up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This room looks like a giant toy box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really pisses me off...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What horridly bad taste he has!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all Pegasus's!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be some awesome rare cards hidden in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.88,0:16:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Solid Vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy, welcome to my private room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This room is the dreamland I hold deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.04,0:16:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why your popularity's been terrible lately...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth {\i1}shut{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.71,0:16:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, Yugi boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you are listening to this message, in all probability, I am no longer safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I anticipated this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our company has already\N been taken over by another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Kaiba Corporation has been bought out by a larger company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:16:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This organization is an underground secretive company that is rumored
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.03,0:17:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to rival even the American supremacy in its brilliance and its influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said "secretive company"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doma is said to act from the shadows, pulling the strings as the puppeteers...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...for thousands of years as the cause of a multitude of financial changes throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You all should have learned this from the text books.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The thriving reign of the Roman Empire, and its sudden downfall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A mere historical repetition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who was {\b0}truly{\b1} responsible for providing the winning side with their weapons during the sailing age?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Civil wars...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was it truly the cause of civilians randomly rebelling against the government?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who was the one to bring the infamous Napoleon to power?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Industrial Revolution that began rising throughout cultures all over the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As well as the Renaissance of the 1800th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who was the one pulling strings during all of these world events from the shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.49,0:18:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do not have any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.20,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because everyone who knew of the real truth were all slaughtered in history's darkest ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I confirmed this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They have been involved in the world's deepest history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Involved in the world's history...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That same Doma has begun to move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are using the power of the Duel Monsters I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, they are aiming for something much larger this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are plotting something far more evil this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plotting...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It shall happen very soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It shall happen very soon, Sir Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thou shalt his soul\N be offered up to our god!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Offered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The soul of the loser shall be offered up to God as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Says he, this world shall be guided down the path of destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be it food to a new, {\b0}pure{\b1} world!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is because I wanted to tell you this that I have called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I hope it is something you can accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hidden within this room is a new card I have created!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Card?!\N -Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In truth, I wanted to hand it to you personally, but it cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will have to find it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.02,0:19:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pot of Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only thing not related to the world of Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WE'LL TAKE IT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WE'LL TAKE IT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange. Nothing's written on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.55,0:19:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even complete yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's just garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nameless card...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.02,0:20:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy, I beg of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please save my cute Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe you, Yugi boy, are the only one who can do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.91,0:20:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An underground organization that's been around for thousands of years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Mai\Nwork with these kind of people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doma is close to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gozaburo once said....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There must be a darkness within the world economy controlling its capital from the shadows."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.62,0:20:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never took them seriously, brushing them off as the heroic words of a coward, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.44,0:20:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! No matter how you struggle, these are opponents you can't reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I can't touch such a huge enemy by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:20:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Claw of Hermos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.30,0:21:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, do you also have a card like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fang of Critias!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the three of us combine our power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.07,0:21:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to defeat Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't the card tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:22:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.03,0:23:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus revealed the true colors of Doma in his projection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If our enemies are really them...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how exactly can we fight them?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our only hope is the three Legendary Dragon cards Yugi, Jounouchi, and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} got from the Duel Monsters world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} help us that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "The Target is the Nameless Pharaoh"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
